				\begin{document}$${i}_{\mathrm{in},\mathrm{ N}}$$\end{document} is the noise current, and BW is the normalized bandwidth.

Therefore, NEP is given in watt per square root of hertz (W/Hz\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
